gudo-Portugal-algarve-beach.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>A less well-known tour is the boat ride upriver to the town of Silves. The scenic cruise takes 1-2 hours, between the river reeds and cute riverside villages of the Algarve. Once you&#x2019;re in Silves, spend some time at the huge red brick castle which sits on top of the hill. The town was once the ancient capital of the Algarve, so it&#x2019;s bursting with history!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/best-places-to-visit-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Best Places to visit in Portugal<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23181104\/Ferragudo-village-Portugal.jpg\" alt=\"Ferragudo village Portugal\"><\/noscript><img width=\"239\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Ferragudo village Portugal\" class=\"wp-image-54330 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1358px) 100vw, 1358px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23181104\/Ferragudo-village-Portugal.jpg 1358w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23181104\/Ferragudo-village-Portugal-424x600.jpg 424w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23181104\/Ferragudo-village-Portugal-573x810.jpg 573w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23181104\/Ferragudo-village-Portugal-239x338.jpg 239w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23181104\/Ferragudo-village-Portugal-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23181104\/Ferragudo-village-Portugal-115x163.jpg 115w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23181104\/Ferragudo-village-Portugal-127x180.jpg 127w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23181104\/Ferragudo-village-Portugal-543x768.jpg 543w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23181104\/Ferragudo-village-Portugal-724x1024.jpg 724w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23181104\/Ferragudo-village-Portugal-764x1080.jpg 764w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23181104\/Ferragudo-village-Portugal-1019x1440.jpg 1019w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23181104\/Ferragudo-village-Portugal-300x424.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23181104\/Ferragudo-village-Portugal-600x848.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23181104\/Ferragudo-village-Portugal-21x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23181104\/Ferragudo-village-Portugal.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-3-explore-forts-and-ruins\">3. Explore Forts and Ruins<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the most unique things about this area is the many cliff-top forts to explore. The most iconic to Ferragudo is the ancient Fort of S&#xE3;o Jo&#xE3;o de Arade. The pale terracotta castle is built into the rock just above the shoreline and was home to the famous Portuguese poet Coelho de Carvalho. Unfortunately, it&#x2019;s not possible to visit inside but the exterior is beautiful enough to make up for it!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>More castles?<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/sintra-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Visit the palaces and castles of Sintra<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n\n<a class=\"block-googlemaps\" title=\"Get our Google Maps Legend\" data-maptype=\"Portugal \" href=\"\/shop\/google-maps\/portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n            <div class=\"block-googlemaps__container\">\n                <div class=\"block-googlemaps__content\">\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__title\">Our Portugal  tips in your Google Maps?<\/span>\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__text\">We made it easier for you! All our tips: favourite to do's, restaurants, hikes, secret spots &amp; more in Google Maps!<\/span>\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__button\">Shop our Maps <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__notice\" style=\"display:none; font-size:12px; margin-top:15px;\">The map for this destination will be available soon. Thank you for your interest!<\/span>\n                <\/div>\n                <img class=\"block-googlemaps__image lazyload\" tempsrc=\"\/build\/images\/google-maps-banner-image.png\" alt=\"google maps phone\">\n            <\/div>\n        <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-4-relax-on-one-of-the-many-beaches\">4. Relax on one of the many beaches<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ferragudo might be technically on the river but it&#x2019;s just around the corner from the windswept Atlantic coastline. Here you&#x2019;ll find yellow sand beaches, clear blue waters, and top surfing spots.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-praia-da-angrinha\"><strong>Praia da Angrinha<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This is the main town beach, sat on the riverside. It&#x2019;s also connected to the Praia Grande, so it&#x2019;s a long stretch of sand divided into two beaches. This means that there&#x2019;s plenty of room to relax and enjoy the views across the river to the marina of Portimao.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also read:&#xA0;<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/beautiful-villages-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Must-see villages in Portugal<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170503\/ferragudo-portugal-beach-algarve.jpg\" alt=\"ferragudo portugal beach algarve\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"ferragudo portugal beach algarve\" class=\"wp-image-54350 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170503\/ferragudo-portugal-beach-algarve.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170503\/ferragudo-portugal-beach-algarve-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170503\/ferragudo-portugal-beach-algarve-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170503\/ferragudo-portugal-beach-algarve-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170503\/ferragudo-portugal-beach-algarve-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170503\/ferragudo-portugal-beach-algarve-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170503\/ferragudo-portugal-beach-algarve-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170503\/ferragudo-portugal-beach-algarve-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170503\/ferragudo-portugal-beach-algarve-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170503\/ferragudo-portugal-beach-algarve-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170503\/ferragudo-portugal-beach-algarve-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170503\/ferragudo-portugal-beach-algarve-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170503\/ferragudo-portugal-beach-algarve-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170503\/ferragudo-portugal-beach-algarve-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170503\/ferragudo-portugal-beach-algarve.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-praia-do-pintadinho\"><strong>Praia do Pintadinho<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This beach is a beautiful sweeping arc of sand, and one of the first beaches as the sea coast begins. It&#x2019;s home to incredible arches and caves which are great for exploring. It&#x2019;s also the perfect spot for swimming.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/50974&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170446\/ferragudo-portugal-village.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170446\/ferragudo-portugal-village-17x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170446\/ferragudo-portugal-village-338x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Ferragudo, Portugal: The Prettiest Village in the Algarve\" height=\"600\" width=\"338\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-praia-dos-caneiros\"><strong>Praia dos Caneiros<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Just a little bit further along is this secluded yellow sand beach, backed by cliffs with caves and rock pools. It also has beautiful views of the lighthouse!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-5-walk-along-the-rugged-coastline\">5. Walk Along the Rugged Coastline<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Symbolic of the Algarve coastline are the impressive cliffs that run for miles and miles on end. This is one of the reasons that it&#x2019;s a top road trip location, as well as being great for hiking. Choose from many cliffside paths that take you to secluded coves, limestone cliffs, and the perfect viewpoints for sundown.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104825\/best-things-to-do-algarve-portugal-saltinourhair-1080x719.jpg\" alt=\"best things to do algarve portugal saltinourhair\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"best things to do algarve portugal saltinourhair\" class=\"wp-image-49088 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104825\/best-things-to-do-algarve-portugal-saltinourhair-1080x719.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104825\/best-things-to-do-algarve-por