.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104825\/best-things-to-do-algarve-portugal-saltinourhair-1080x719.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>A popular walk is the one to the charming Ferragudo Lighthouse (Ponta do Altar), just a 20-minutes from the center of town. The little white cottage with its red signal tower sits on the cliff edge with views that stretch out down the coastline.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Hire bikes and cycle here at sunrise or sunset for pretty views over the ocean.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170508\/Algarve-coastline-ferragudo-portugal.jpg\" alt=\"Algarve coastline ferragudo portugal\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Algarve coastline ferragudo portugal\" class=\"wp-image-54346 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170508\/Algarve-coastline-ferragudo-portugal.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170508\/Algarve-coastline-ferragudo-portuga