altinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170508\/Algarve-coastline-ferragudo-portugal.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-6-enjoy-atlantic-watersports\">6. Enjoy Atlantic Watersports<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Algarve is the home of watersports, famous for its waves and winds that make it a surfing hot spot. Ferragudo is a great base to explore all the best surfing spots, especially if you have a campervan.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>If adrenaline sports aren&#x2019;t really your thing, opt for the more tranquil option of paddleboarding. Paddle peacefully along the deep blue shoreline, stopping for breaks in the caves or finding a remote rock to sunbathe for a while. Snorkeling is also an option, as there are many beaches with transparent waters, underground caves, and colorful marine life.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"transport\">How to visit Ferragudo<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ferragudo is only a 50-minute drive from the international airport in Faro. It&#x2019;s also possible to take a train from Faro to Portimao: the town which sits across the water from Ferragudo. It&#x2019;s possible to take a 10-minute water taxi from Portimao to Ferragudo.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#x2019;re staying in Lagos and visiting Ferragudo as a day trip, it&#x2019;s a 40-minute drive. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Planning to visit Portugal by car? We recommend renting a car through <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a> as they work with local car rental companies. When booking through <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a>, all the insurances are included in the price you see on the website.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-getting-around\">Getting Around<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Once in Ferragudo, it&#x2019;s super easy to explore on foot or by bicycle. This is a great way to see the beautiful fishing village and find all the secret corners of the local beaches.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have a campervan\/car this gives you the freedom to explore the surrounding areas around Ferragudo. For example, great surfing spots that sit a little further down the coastline.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Here&#x2019;s how to:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/travel-portugal-campervan\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Travel Portugal by campervan<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23170458\/ferragudo-portugal-cute-streets.jpg\" alt=\"ferragudo portugal cute streets\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"ferragudo portugal cute stree